---
title: Veggie Mince & Cherry Tomato Ragu with Gnocchi & Baby Spinach Leaves
description: It’s always a good night when pasta is on the menu, especially with the pillows of gnocchi. Make it a vegetarian
extravaganza with tender cherry tomato ragu and veggie mince. It’s one to remember!
